                          <note>
                            Corresponding to <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/NS8WNSR6"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Budge1929"/><title level="m">The Bandlet of Righteousness, an Ethiopian Book of the Dead: The Ethiopic Text of the ልፋፈ፡ ጽድቅ፡ in Facsimile from Two Manuscripts in the British Museum</title><title level="s">Luzac’s Semitic Text &amp; Translation Series</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Ernest Alfred Wallis</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Budge</t:surname></author><pubPlace>London</pubPlace><publisher>Luzac &amp; Company</publisher><date>1929</date><series><t:title xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" level="s">Luzac’s Semitic Text &amp; Translation Series</t:title><t:biblScope xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" unit="volume">19</t:biblScope></series><biblScope unit="volume">19</biblScope><citedRange unit="page">67 l. 6</citedRange></bibl>.</note>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.13">
                          <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6967PrayerPassion">Prayer on the Passion of Jesus Christ, which Jesus
          revealed to Matilda, Bridget and Elizabeth</title>
                          <textLang mainLang="gez"/>         
                          <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                            በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ዜና፡ <sic>ሕማማቲከ፡</sic> ለእግዚአብሔር፨ አምላክነ፡ 
                            ወመድኃኒነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፨ ሰዶር፡ አላዶር፨ ደናት፨ አ<choice><corr resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices">ዴ</corr><sic>ዲ</sic></choice>ራ፡ 
                            ሮዳስ፡ ወ፭ቅንዋተ፡ መስቀሉ፡ ለእግዚእነ፡ ወመድኃኒነ፡ ኢ<supplied reason="omitted">የ</supplied>ሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ በዝንቱ፨ ሕማምከ፡ ዕቀበኒ፡ ወአድኅነኒ፨ 
                            ለገብርከ።
                          </incipit>
                        </msItem>
                      </msItem>
